window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Watch </b><b><i>Silo</i></b><b>, the Apple TV+ series based on the bestselling Silo Saga!</b></p> <p><b><i>Wool</i></b><b> introduced the world of the silo. </b><b><i>Shift</i></b><b> told the story of its creation. </b><b><i>Dust</i></b><b> will describe its downfall.</b></p> <p>Juliette, now mayor of Silo 18, doesn’t trust Silo 1, especially its leader, Donald. But in the world of the Silos, there is no black and white—everything is shades of gray. Donald may not be the monster Juliette thinks he is, and may in fact be key to humanity’s continued survival. But can they work together long enough to succeed?</p>"; 
